OL,3,CHouse explosion which hospitalised
OL,4,Cfour people caused by gas build-up
OL,6,FAn explosion which partially destroyed
OL,7,Fa family home in Jersey was caused by
OL,8,Fgas.
OL,10,FFour people were hospitalised after
OL,11,Fthe major incident at Mont Pinel, St
OL,12,FSaviour, in June with the Fire Service
OL,13,Fnow stating it is "reasonable to
OL,14,Fconclude that an explosion occured due
OL,15,Fto ignition of a mixture of a
OL,16,Fflammable gas and air that accumulated
OL,17,Fwithin the property".
