OL,3,CHouse explosion which hospitalised
OL,4,Cfour people caused by gas build-up
OL,6,FIt follows an initial investigation by
OL,7,Fthe island's Health and Safety
OL,8,FInspectorate which is still continuing
OL,9,Finto why the incident took place.
OL,11,FJersey Fire adds that loss adjusters
OL,12,Fcan now access the affected properties
OL,13,Fto help insurers assess the cost of
OL,14,Fthe damage and families to return to
OL,15,Ftheir homes.
OL,17,FAt the time of the explosion, Island
OL,18,FEnergy said no gas leak was found in
OL,19,Fthe areas that they were allowed to
OL,20,Fsurvey.
