OL,3,CHouse explosion which hospitalised
OL,4,Cfour people caused by gas build-up
OL,6,FIn response to this development, it
OL,7,Fexplains: "We acknowledge the results
OL,8,Fof the investigation and continue to
OL,9,Fwork with the relevant authorities
OL,10,Fregarding the incident in the vicinity
OL,11,Fof Le Mont Pinel.
OL,13,F"We are unable to comment further
OL,14,Funtil we receive the forensic results
OL,15,Fof the Health and Safety Inspectorate
OL,16,Freport."
OL,18,FThe utility company adds that it will
OL,19,Fbe carrying out an additional survey
OL,20,Fof the gas network as part of a
OL,21,Fbroader safety programme in Jersey.
