OL,6,FJersey's Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,7,FFarnham, does say: "We would like to
OL,8,Fthank the States of Jersey Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service and Health and Safety
OL,10,FInspectorate for their investigations
OL,11,Finto the explosion at Mont Pinel.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts remain with all those
OL,14,Fimpacted and the Government continues
OL,15,Fto provide support and guidance to all
OL,16,Faffected by the incident."
